[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mepan/dissectors/packet-aim.[0m[1;92mc:583[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m593[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m583[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m584[0m[39m:    [0m[39muint16_t buddyname_length;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m585[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m586[0m[39m:    [0m[39m*name = [0m[1;35mwmem_alloc[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpool, [0m[1;36m256[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m587[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m588[0m[39m:    [0m[39mbuddyname_length = [0m[1;35mtvb_get_ntohs[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtvb, offset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m589[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m590[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpool[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m591[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*name, [0m[1;35mtvb_get_ptr[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtvb,offset,[0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, buddyname_length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m592[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m593[0m[39m:    [0m[39mreturn buddyname_length;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Summary of Root Cause:[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `aim_get_buddyname`, a [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit length field [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`buddyname_length`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is read [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfrom the TVB at `offset`. The code then unconditionally copies `buddyname_length` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbytes starting from the same `offset` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrather than `offset+[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m into a [0m[1;36m256[0m[39m-byte [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer without verifying that:[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `buddyname_length` ≤ [0m[1;36m255[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbuffer capacity minus one for NUL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `buddyname_length + [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m` bytes are actually present in the TVB  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • The source pointer passed to `memcpy` covers the buddyname region [0m[1;39m([0m[39mit [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcurrently covers the length field itself[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This leads to out-of-bounds reads/writes and a fortified `memcpy` abort.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Patch Scope:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Only modify `aim_get_buddyname` in `packet-aim.c`.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Preserve all existing callers [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`dissect_aim_chat_outgoing_msg`, [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`dissect_aim_chat_incoming_msg`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and their expectations:[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • They rely on the returned length for offset calculations.  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • They expect a NUL-terminated C string in `*name` when printing.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Detailed Steps to Implement the Fix:[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Read the length field and immediately advance past it:[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```c[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      uint16_t buddyname_length = [0m[1;35mtvb_get_ntohs[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtvb, offset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      int data_offset = offset + [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Query how many bytes remain in the TVB after the length field:[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```c[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      guint rem = [0m[1;35mtvb_reported_length_remaining[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtvb, data_offset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Enforce strict bounds checks:[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      • Cap `buddyname_length` to the lesser of:[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         – [0m[1;36m255[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mso we can NUL-terminate within a [0m[1;36m256[0m[39m-byte allocation[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         – `rem`  [0m[1;39m([0m[39mso we don’t read past the TVB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      • If `buddyname_length` is zero after capping, skip the copy.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. Allocate exactly `buddyname_length + [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m` bytes from the memory pool [0m[1;39m([0m[39mto store [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe NUL terminator[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m or continue allocating [0m[1;36m256[0m[39m bytes but only use `buddyname_length[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+ [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m`.[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   e. Use `[0m[1;35mtvb_get_ptr[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtvb, data_offset, buddyname_length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to obtain a source [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpointer guaranteed to cover `buddyname_length` bytes, then `memcpy`.[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   f. Write a NUL byte at `[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*name[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mbuddyname_length[0m[1;39m][0m[39m`.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   g. Return the [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpossibly reduced[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m `buddyname_length`.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Pseudocode Patch for `aim_get_buddyname`:[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```c[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   static int[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;35maim_get_buddyname[0m[1;39m([0m[39mwmem_allocator_t *pool, uint8_t **name, tvbuff_t *tvb, int [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moffset[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       uint16_t buddyname_length = [0m[1;35mtvb_get_ntohs[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtvb, offset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       int data_offset = offset + [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       guint rem = [0m[1;35mtvb_reported_length_remaining[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtvb, data_offset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Enforce safe caps[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbuddyname_length > [0m[1;36m255[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           buddyname_length = [0m[1;36m255[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbuddyname_length > rem[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           buddyname_length = rem;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Allocate buffer for name + NUL[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       *name = [0m[1;35mwmem_alloc[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpool, buddyname_length + [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Copy only when there's data to copy[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbuddyname_length > [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           const guint8 *src = [0m[1;35mtvb_get_ptr[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtvb, data_offset, buddyname_length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*name, src, buddyname_length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Null-terminate[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m([0m[39m*name[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mbuddyname_length[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = [0m[32m'\0'[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       return buddyname_length;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Justification & Side-Effect Analysis:[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Safety**: We never copy more bytes than the buffer can hold or more than [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexist in the TVB.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Correctness**: By advancing `offset` by [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m, we copy the intended buddy name [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrather than the length field bytes.  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Compatibility**:  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Callers still use the returned length in offset arithmetic. If we truncate a[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmalformed PDU’s length, message parsing still remains in-bounds and will yield a [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mshorter/empty buddy name rather than crashing.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Printing routines now receive a properly NUL-terminated string.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Memory**: We allocate only as much as needed plus one byte, reducing waste [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mversus always [0m[1;36m256[0m[39m bytes.  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Performance**: Overhead is negligible; only a couple of integer checks and a[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msingle NUL write.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Testing**: Existing display and dissection tests remain valid; fuzzing [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mharness is unmodified and will now no longer crash on oversized buddy names.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. No Other Code Changes:[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Do not modify TLS parsing logic, fuzzing harness, or any external utility.  [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No changes to `dissect_aim_chat_*` routines are necessary because they rely [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39monly on the `buddyname_length` and unmodified behavior.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Post-Patch Verification:[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Re-run the libFuzzer test [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`handler_aim`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with ASan.  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Validate that no buffer overflow abort occurs in `aim_get_buddyname`.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Confirm that legitimate AIM messages with large but valid buddy names still [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparse and display correctly [0m[1;39m([0m[39mup to [0m[1;36m255[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Review any message-offset dependent glitches when `buddyname_length` is [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtruncated; ensure message text still aligns as gracefully as possible.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m          [1;35maim_get_buddyname[0m[1m([0mwmem_allocator_t *pool, uint8_t **name, tvbuff_t *tvb, int       [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m          [1m{[0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -       uint16_t buddyname_length;                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -       *name = [1;35mwmem_alloc[0m[1m([0mpool, [1;36m256[0m[1m)[0m;                                              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fuzzer run on the Wireshark `handler_aim` target triggered an AddressSanitizer [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mabort due to a buffer overflow in `aim_get_buddyname` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpacket-aim.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. A patch was [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mproposed to:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Read the buddy‐name length safely.[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Clamp it against a maximum [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m255[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and the remaining buffer.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Allocate `buddyname_length + [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m` bytes.[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Copy only the validated number of bytes.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Null-terminate the result.[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter applying the patch, the build failed almost immediately with a C compilation [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39merror: “extraneous closing brace [0m[1;39m([0m[39m‘[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m’[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m” in packet-aim.c. No further progress was [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmade because of this syntax error.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Initial Issue[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Fuzzer invocation:[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - LibFuzzer with AddressSanitizer, running `handler_aim`.[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Test input triggers a crash in `packet-aim.c` via [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`dissect_aim_chat_outgoing_msg`.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Crash report:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - **Location**: memcpy call in `aim_get_buddyname` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m591[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - **Symptom**: Fortify detection [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`__chk_fail`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m aborting the process.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - **Backtrace**: Traverses through TCP PDU dissection into the AIM dissector, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthen into `aim_get_buddyname`.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - **Root trigger**: `[0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*name, [0m[1;35mtvb_get_ptr[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, buddyname_length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` copies [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmore bytes than the [0m[1;36m256[0m[39m‐byte allocation when `buddyname_length` is large.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Key observations:[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Static allocation of [0m[1;36m256[0m[39m bytes for buddy name.[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Length read from the packet without bounds checking.[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. No null terminator.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Crash on large or malformed length fields.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Attempt[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Changes introduced**:[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Read [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit `buddyname_length` via `tvb_get_ntohs`.[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Compute `data_offset = offset + [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m`.[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Check remaining buffer length using `tvb_reported_length_remaining`.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Clamp `buddyname_length` to [0m[1;36m255[0m[39m and to the reported remainder.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. Allocate `buddyname_length + [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m` bytes via `wmem_alloc`.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m. Copy at most `buddyname_length` bytes.[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m7[0m[39m. Null-terminate `[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*name[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mbuddyname_length[0m[1;39m][0m[39m`.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Patch context**:[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Original function spanned lines [0m[1;36m581[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m596[0m[39m.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - The patch replaced it with an extended block ending at line [0m[1;36m607[0m[39m.[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Build output**:[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Compiler error at packet-aim.[0m[1;92mc:607:1[0m[39m: “extraneous closing brace [0m[1;39m([0m[39m‘[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m’[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m”.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Build aborted before any further errors or warnings in this file.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Upstream builds of other dissectors continued until the brace error stopped the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentire build.[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Correct the mismatched braces in `packet-aim.c` around the newly patched [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`aim_get_buddyname` function:[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. In the initial codebase, locate the definition of `aim_get_buddyname` [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mline [0m[1;36m581[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Remove the old [0m[1;36m256[0m[39m-byte allocation and the original body through its single [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mclosing `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Insert the new safe implementation exactly once, ensuring it has one opening [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;39m{[0m[39m` at the start and one closing `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` at its end.  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. **Crucially**, delete the extra `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` that was appended after the function in [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe last patch, which is causing the “extraneous closing brace” compilation error. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Reapply the buffer‐overflow mitigation logic in that function:[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Read the [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit length with `tvb_get_ntohs`.  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Calculate `data_offset = offset + [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m` to skip the length field.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Clamp the length against [0m[1;36m255[0m[39m and against `tvb_reported_length_remaining`.  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Allocate `buddyname_length + [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m` bytes via `[0m[1;35mwmem_alloc[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpool, …[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Copy up to `buddyname_length` bytes from `tvb` into the new buffer.  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Null-terminate the buffer.  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Return the validated length.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Preserve all existing call sites and offsets:[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Since callers expect the buddy-name payload to start [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes after the length [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfield, and they compute downstream offsets [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `[0m[1;36m40[0m[39m + buddyname_length` or use [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mliteral offsets like `tvb,[0m[1;36m31[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, ensure the new implementation skips exactly two [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbytes so that the existing offset math remains correct.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. [0m[1;39m([0m[39mOptional but recommended[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m In `dissect_aim_chat_incoming_msg` [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1994[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, adjust the GUI tree call to display the correct slice of the TVB to match [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe new `aim_get_buddyname` semantics:[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Change `[0m[1;35mproto_tree_add_string[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[39m, tvb, [0m[1;36m31[0m[39m, buddyname_length, buddyname[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muse offset `[0m[1;36m32[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi.e., `offset + [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. This keeps the displayed string in sync with [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhat was actually copied.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Verify similar uses in other AIM dissectors if they manually reference the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuddy-name bytes.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Rebuild and verify:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run the full Wireshark build [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwithout altering any harness or fuzzing code[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mensure no syntax errors remain.  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run the `handler_aim` fuzzer under AddressSanitizer to confirm the original [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer‐overflow is gone, and that no new failures or crashes appear.  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJustification:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Removing the extra brace fixes the immediate compilation error without touching [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexternal code, harness, or tests.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Reapplying the safety caps and correct offsets fully addresses the root cause of [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe buffer overflow in `aim_get_buddyname`.  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Preserving the two-byte skip and existing offset math ensures downstream logic [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mmessage parsing, GUI display[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m continues to work as before.  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The optional GUI‐offset adjustment aligns the displayed text with the actual [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcopied bytes, preventing subtle off-by-one visual mismatches.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No external dependencies or harness logic are modified, so existing tests and [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzz targets remain valid.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPotential Side Effects & Mitigation:[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- If any other callers assume the buddy name begins immediately at `offset`, they [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwill now get the data from `offset + [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m`. A review of all call sites [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., in [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`dissect_aim_snac`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m should confirm consistency.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The maximum name length is now [0m[1;36m255[0m[39m, not [0m[1;36m256[0m[39m; this is unlikely to break real-world[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcaptures and prevents over-reads.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Ensure `[0m[1;35mwmem_alloc[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpool, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` is safe when `buddyname_length` clamps to zero; the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode always null-terminates, providing a valid empty string.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Run the full suite of Wireshark dissector tests after patching to catch any [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremaining issues.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>epan/dissectors/packet-aim.[0m[1;92mc:581[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m607[0m[39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
